{"tid":1220132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我地不擇手段， 就會變成土共一樣","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:01:21.000Z","uid":106043,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f316a5b7a881011b275d2381966a03076469fca9","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:52:02.000Z","msg":"近幾日reddit好多香港post收大量嘅外國人關注同留言。<br />\n其中有幾句對答我覺得十分之啱同覺得係十分之代表到普世價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n有人討論到中國個發展同運作，講到啲不道德嘅手法時， 一個鬼佬講大陸追求instant result。<br />\n<br />\n我地要減少敵人， 增加同伴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>我哋用人哋本聖經，就係踐踏緊人哋嘅信仰同唔尊重佢哋。</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聖經有冇效? 好撚勁<br />\n但係一濫用聖經就好似土共咁，  不擇手段追求instant success, 係絕對唔道德</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道德高地同國際輿論不可失一， 我地要用老毛果套&quot;統戰&quot;， 聯合砌低主要敵人</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cbf5a27154cd56f3dba4fdf8e8709eaf0aab98","tid":1220132,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fd17e1997c98e4d4267627f84ae2bde5c982d67","tid":1220132,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"點撚樣濫用聖經呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教徒唱聖詩感化暴徒都叫濫用？<br />\n唱聖詩諗經文都唔得點傳道呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9667f7853eb702631399dcdffd83fb06ab95f4","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fd17e1997c98e4d4267627f84ae2bde5c982d67","tid":1220132,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"點撚樣濫用聖經呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教徒唱聖詩感化暴徒都叫濫用？<br />\n唱聖詩諗經文都唔得點傳道呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"你真係基督教徒嘅，用又點話。<br />\n但係一堆人借聖經過橋擺明當免死金牌就一眼比人睇得出。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下前幾日大部分人都係就咁樣上街， 只有少部分人係有唱聖詩甚至更小部分有拎聖經 。<br />\n然後點會今日無啦啦大部分人會拎住本聖經唱聖詩呢。"},{"pid":"82b71755d3f168b4bd9f3f81c1840762431c37f7","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔夠clickbait 冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ea75d7af34aeb6a534acdeb1903d0166c89f36","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"希望大家明白唔用聖經唔係因為單單會激嬲基督徒，而係道德原則上會令我地變得同中共一樣。<br />\n<br />\n仲會畀位人入添， 基督徒&gt;西方宗教&gt;外國勢力"},{"pid":"9f1b229d88a0d377d688db83470e1ced2a43a08b","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:20:09.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩宗教呀"},{"pid":"05da146a23644010297867c2011e2eb9b7255741","tid":1220132,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"一句講晒，唔係教徒就唔好去使用聖經"},{"pid":"de9680571b48e48466332b3b630e46d26c3ed33f","tid":1220132,"uid":106043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩宗教呀"},{"pid":"57d261aaa43e908e96b946c53ff746be88e4f95f","tid":1220132,"uid":248540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"會好似佢地一樣取得政權？？<br />\n美國立國唔係靠獨立戰爭？點解